import { useState } from "react"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import axios from "axios"; function Payment() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [success, setSuccess] = useState(false); const sendMessage = () => { setSuccess(false); axios.post("http://localhost:5010/api/sendMessage", { fromPlanet: localStorage.getItem("fromPlanet"), toPlanet: localStorage.getItem("toPlanet"), date: localStorage.getItem("date"), price: localStorage.getItem("price"), flight: localStorage.getItem("flight"), time: localStorage.getItem("time"), no }).then((res) => { console.log(res); }).catch((err) => { console.log(err); }); navigate('/') } return ( <> {!success ?

Please Enter your Card Details

Total Amount Payable: {localStorage.getItem("price")}

If you have a Space Membership ID, enter it now to earn 1500 Spacial points
: (

Payment Successful!!

We will only use your number to send the booking details
)} ); } export default Payment;
